{"tid":895234,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]而家打工仔搵食艱難，做嘢都要比人兇","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T13:07:54.000Z","uid":59123,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50de253247e649f866927229350fbd933a2ec541","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:32:10.000Z","msg":"啫係呢，我打工抄門牌嘅啫。<br />\n<br />\n要老爆你要收你地就唔會明目張膽咁喺你面前同你鳩撚咁<br />\n<br />\n嗡咁多嘢，制服pass係基本嘢，但散工無。ok呢樣我唔<br />\n<br />\n著，所以我派返公司卡片比你，你就喺左閪右閪咁撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n私人地方？條街唔係人地屋唔係你間屋又無閘叫私人地<br />\n<br />\n方？你比錢買咗？然後仲要叫我除帽同問我袋有乜？<br />\n<br />\n都係果句，我要老爆你我仲唔走仲要浪費我時間精神心力<br />\n<br />\n比你喺度閪？<br />\n<br />\n不知所謂。真係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n仲話我鬼撚祟祟，我呢就光明正大咁行嘅，要鬼祟我見到<br />\n<br />\n你就陃埋或者好驚啦，啱唔啱呀掃管笏村第三區某居民。"},{"pid":"f193b709bf977e377cbdefd3ab82fd4268372303","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"同埋，<br />\n<br />\n你泊架綿羊仔喺一條比人行嘅走廊又啱唔啱？<br />\n<br />\n仲要整個閘霸多啲條大路位又啱唔啱？<br />\n<br />\n50步笑100步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b3a1323148cf3e47231fc24d220dab24bf45e8","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"你話我鬼撚祟祟係撚咁影，<br />\n<br />\n其實我影大路塊爛地你已經衝咗出來。<br />\n<br />\n基本上，影之前我係會知會屋主。<br />\n<br />\n但，塊爛地又唔係你嘅，<br />\n<br />\n而且我又未入私人地段，你講經？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打埋比老細，比你同佢對話埋，<br />\n<br />\n都重複，我點知你係咪老爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係你僭建霸路驚我督你灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查實我就抄門牌嘅啫，你僭唔僭建關我閪事？<br />\n<br />\n臨走仲叫我唔好整古做怪，<br />\n<br />\n我光明正大行大路架喎，有人問我答，<br />\n<br />\n搞返清楚先"},{"pid":"9f086906240e15714ca6220225f26c0d50d13edb","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"如果大家有興趣，<br />\n<br />\n可以打1823去舉報佢，<br />\n<br />\n不過成日話線路繁忙。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家集個氣。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，<br />\n<br />\n就係咁多呢啲村屋撚樣生人霸死地，<br />\n<br />\n但又唔起屋，<br />\n<br />\n先會無地起樓。"},{"pid":"b3e01dbc10cf4d12c689e90c514a04ea71fc10ef","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"background?"},{"pid":"534a204dd9cfea3244f90d17f85a81ead8ed3861","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3e01dbc10cf4d12c689e90c514a04ea71fc10ef","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"background?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"個人背景定個地方？"},{"pid":"4c95e23d24cb472cfbf1c671c47b2a84c3f15eed","tid":895234,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"即場屌左未"},{"pid":"0cc781ca9baaaf165165423f68c434bc6715c56d","tid":895234,"uid":51105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"一句句子都要隔行，好睇啲？"},{"pid":"fd944be592a0a97b7c2299cb5d7c2ce6fae680be","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"534a204dd9cfea3244f90d17f85a81ead8ed3861","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3e01dbc10cf4d12c689e90c514a04ea71fc10ef","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"background?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"個人背景定個地方？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"件事 你做咩工"},{"pid":"726ff2c16b16f24613d13b53b1cf73e6e48a22e3","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4c95e23d24cb472cfbf1c671c47b2a84c3f15eed","tid":895234,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"即場屌左未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"有，<br />\n<br />\n我一句得埋去(得左兩次，一次係佢同老細對話緊)<br />\n<br />\n我要老爆，<br />\n<br />\n我洗乜曬口水又派卡片又打比老細？<br />\n<br />\n我收地嘅，<br />\n<br />\n又點會一個人黎咁搏。<br />\n<br />\n然後他就繼續話:鬼撚祟祟，古靈精怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fc6129d3a83efb1011f81dbbb8c2c22c11e84b","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726ff2c16b16f24613d13b53b1cf73e6e48a22e3","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4c95e23d24cb472cfbf1c671c47b2a84c3f15eed","tid":895234,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"即場屌左未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"有，<br />\n<br />\n我一句得埋去(得左兩次，一次係佢同老細對話緊)<br />\n<br />\n我要老爆，<br />\n<br />\n我洗乜曬口水又派卡片又打比老細？<br />\n<br />\n我收地嘅，<br />\n<br />\n又點會一個人黎咁搏。<br />\n<br />\n然後他就繼續話:鬼撚祟祟，古靈精怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"用無人機影啦"},{"pid":"530466ecc1c66bf706b987f067a6185844e4941d","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd944be592a0a97b7c2299cb5d7c2ce6fae680be","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"534a204dd9cfea3244f90d17f85a81ead8ed3861","tid":895234,"uid":59123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3e01dbc10cf4d12c689e90c514a04ea71fc10ef","tid":895234,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"background?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"個人背景定個地方？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"件事 你做咩工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"我交代含糊，請各大佬受小弟一拜。<br />\n<br />\n事緣我就係幫一間測量師行做pt，工作內容係入圍村或者村屋抄門牌。咁每一次做之前，老細都會知會該村村長，以避免不必要麻煩。而要做嘅嘢就係用公司手機影該村屋信箱或門牌然後記錄低。<br />\n<br />\n有咩用？就係update返啲網上地圖，方便郵差同救護人員搵地址。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，今日就去屯門掃管笏村做嘢。咁我落車喺村第三區小巴站落車。request同通知一聲祠堂個阿叔後就開始工作。之後，就有個阿叔喺遠處衝過黎。<br />\n<br />\n一黎就好唔善意:鬼撚祟祟咁影乜撚嘢？想老爆？<br />\n<br />\n然後就如上述。"},{"pid":"c8aeb570ec001c7d137